highlights.text: “Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 151 weeks straight.
J Balvin has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “RITMO (Bad Boys For Life)” is the highest at #9.
“Ayy Macarena” by Tyga is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 84 spots at #75.
“Vete” by Bad Bunny is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #10.
